## Task 4 — Key Concepts Summary

| Term | Definition |
|---|---|
| Operating System (OS) | Core software that manages hardware, applications, and all system resources |
| Kernel space | Privileged OS area with direct hardware access — home of the kernel |
| User space | Area where regular applications run with limited permissions |
| GUI | Visual interface — windows, icons, menus — interaction via clicking |
| CLI | Text-based interface — type commands for precision and speed |
